{"tid":2320412,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"由三寶trans社科","createTime":"2020-12-10T20:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T08:03:22.000Z","uid":262886,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fed10cc121b1e27382e2449a9f5660bf6e1d0289","tid":2320412,"uid":262886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:16:30.000Z","msg":"讀咗兩年三寶，因為健康原因<br />\n由專科轉讀社科，依家讀緊心理學<br />\n轉之前雖然好多人話我笨柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但自己真係頂唔順，所以最後都堅決轉科<br />\n讀得開心咗好多，依家就grad<br />\n亦準備要出嚟乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家開始唔知未來路向，諗住讀埋master <br />\n想讀返心理學相關嘅科，但唔大興趣做research<br />\n知自己唔夠料做Clinical psy ，唔夠人爭<br />\n想問Master可以有咩好揀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴絲比啲意見我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e184ad5ab9ea52f5594e6d2bccc947f1084115bd","tid":2320412,"uid":65201,"like":28,"dislike":4,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:19:42.000Z","msg":"全香港得你一個on9得過林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ed6afa65900b8876a5a8c8e804c50e84a61895","tid":2320412,"uid":262886,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"e184ad5ab9ea52f5594e6d2bccc947f1084115bd","tid":2320412,"uid":65201,"like":28,"dislike":4,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:19:42.000Z","msg":"全香港得你一個on9得過林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:28:05.000Z","msg":"我都知自己on9，有機會讀都唔讀埋去<img src=\"/assets/